 .../net/wireless/intel/iwlwifi/pcie/tx-gen2.c |  5 +++--
 drivers/net/wireless/intel/iwlwifi/pcie/tx.c  | 20 +++++++++++--------
 3 files changed, 18 insertions(+), 12 deletions(-)

